msg: QPID-1634 : FileQueueBackingStore had two issues. Delete wasn't using the getFileHandle() method so it was attempting to delete a bin rather than the message data. Our Broker Unit tests don't create the right type of ByteBuffer so whilst they passed the buffer.getData().array() failed as array() is not supported in the ByteBuffer types we actually use at runtime.
